<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Activate Your Forecastly Account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #4A5568;
            background-color: #FAFAFC;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5E60CE 0%, #56CFE1 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #5E60CE;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #718096;
            background-color: #F7FAFC;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://forecastly.online/template/img/forecastly_logo_64x64.png" width="24px" height="24px" alt="Forecastly" style="border:0; display:inline-block;" />
            <span>Forecastly</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Activate Your Account</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{ customer.firstName }} {{ customer.lastName }},</p>

        <p>Thank you for creating a Forecastly account! To complete your registration and start using our financial planning tools, please activate your account by clicking the button below:</p>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ url('activate_account', {'token': activationToken}) }}" class="button">
                Activate Account
            </a>
        </p>

        <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
            <code>{{ url('activate_account', {'token': activationToken}) }}</code>
        </p>

        <p>This activation link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.</p>

        <p>If you didn't create an account with Forecastly, please ignore this email.</p>

        <p>Welcome aboard,<br>The Forecastly Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Forecastly by Meridian Wealth Technologies, LLC. All rights reserved.</p>

        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="{{ url('privacy_policy') }}">Privacy Policy</a> |
            <a href="{{ url('terms_of_service') }}">Terms of Service</a> |
            <a href="{{ url('main_contact_support') }}">Contact Us</a>
        </div>

        <p>Meridian Wealth Technologies, LLC<br>
            600 West Broadway Suite 700-100A PMB 70148<br>
            San Diego, CA 92101</p>

        <p><em>This is a transactional email related to your account. You're receiving this because you signed up for Forecastly.</em></p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>